This paper is primarily focused on software maintenance, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The paper also discusses the use of metadata and dependency graphs, which are common topics in programming languages (cs.PL) and software design (cs.SD). The use of distributed version control systems and the management of multiple branches may also fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed computing (cs.DC).
